oop-dogg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ed-sheeran-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ed-sheeran-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位创作型歌手透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">艾德·希兰</a>烟瘾不大，但他无法抗拒和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">《史努比狗狗》</a>一起抽烟。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-autumn-variations-review-lyrics-tracklist-3505933">艾德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）——“秋季变奏”评论：南瓜香料小睡</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位“Thinking Out Loud”歌手兼词曲作者在<em>《柯南需要朋友》</em>播客中接受柯南·奥布莱恩采访时表示，今年三月，他在澳大利亚墨尔本罗德·拉沃尔竞技场表演后在后台遇见了史努比狗狗。</p><p>希兰是通过另一位著名朋友罗素·克劳 (Russell Crowe) 介绍给史努比的，罗素·克劳碰巧参加了希兰在墨尔本的演出。 “多年来，我和罗素·克劳是非常亲密的朋友，他和史努比狗狗也非常亲密。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CpYOY66LIrG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://w